com.jme3.renderer.opengl

Interface GLFbo

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AndroidGL, GLDebugDesktop, GLDebugES, IosGL, JoglGLFbo, LwjglGLFboEXT, LwjglGLFboGL3

    public interface GLFbo
    Framebuffer object functions. Available by default in OpenGL ES 2, but on desktop GL 2 an extension is required.
